                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell/>
                                    <cell rendition="#right">Total</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">$549,800,000</cell>
                                </row>
                            </table>
                            <p>II. Budgetary Expenditures Allocable to War Against Japan: <table cols="3" rows="2">
