                                        <cell/>
                                        <cell rend="padding-left: 2.5em">1941 dollars</cell>
                                        <cell role="num">86,700,000,000</cell>
                                    </row>
                                </table></p>
                            <p>III. Costs of Japanese Occupation: <seg rend="float:right;">None</seg></p>
                            <p>IV. Man-years of Armed Forces: <seg rend="padding-left: 2.5em">16,753,000</seg></p>
                            <p>V. Human Casualties: <table cols="3" rend="width: 50%" rendition="#center-block" rows="2">
